    },
    "b-is2-opener-1": {
      "id": "b-is2-opener-1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "A document is one canonical state that neither reader touches directly. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mruswus2-10-uqq1wb": {
      "id": "pm-mruswus2-10-uqq1wb",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "That state is a translation layer between humans and AI"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mruswus2-11-h370rw": {
      "id": "pm-mruswus2-11-h370rw",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Each reader meets it through a renderer that speaks its language, and changes it through interactions built for how it works. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrusksy4-1-vk2unu": {
      "id": "pm-mrusksy4-1-vk2unu",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "This section defines the idea and the contract between the surfaces; each surface's own doc goes deeper."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp81bx4-2839-23vo4v": {
      "id": "pm-mrp81bx4-2839-23vo4v",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The Issue"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpfasf5-1-dsblal": {
      "id": "pm-mrpfasf5-1-dsblal",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The issue is that people are trying to fit the same medium to both humans and agents, even though we have very different optimal information consumption methods"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpe42kc-17-869urm": {
      "id": "pm-mrpe42kc-17-869urm",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Humans",
          "attributes": {
            "bold": true
          }
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-766-1z1inz": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-766-1z1inz",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Text is a great medium, but people learn and understand much more when you can use multiple senses "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-767-o2h9xx": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-767-o2h9xx",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "HTML is good as this allows for making significantly better visualizations"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-768-17aomg": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-768-17aomg",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Agents",
          "attributes": {
            "bold": true
          }
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-769-jbnmhs": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-769-jbnmhs",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Excel at text but lacking in the visual space"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpfasf5-2-p1nfqi": {
      "id": "pm-mrpfasf5-2-p1nfqi",
      "type": "divider",
      "props": {},
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpfasf5-3-zz5vtb": {
      "id": "pm-mrpfasf5-3-zz5vtb",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Markdown has been the standard for interacting with agents, and for good reason"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpd2dxn-75-25vx8w": {
      "id": "pm-mrpd2dxn-75-25vx8w",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Models operate largely in a text based world and simple text system allow for huge gains"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-758-bfk1ce": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-758-bfk1ce",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Markdown is not good for human readers, especially as the size of documents grows"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-759-au9dee": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-759-au9dee",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "I have found myself many a time just not reading the MD docs at all as the UX for it is terrible"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-760-2e5vcv": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-760-2e5vcv",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Recently HTML or MDX have been touted as the best way to do it, which has merit, but has flaws"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-761-qj4gpg": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-761-qj4gpg",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Extra tokens for HTML and no easy way to edit the components"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-762-pil9qz": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-762-pil9qz",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Similar issue with MDX"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpfkxn0-75-76u4o2": {
      "id": "pm-mrpfkxn0-75-76u4o2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The key idea we need to accept is that AI and humans consume information differently, so there is no true single medium that is best for both of use."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpddwdu-763-0b5gwr": {
      "id": "pm-mrpddwdu-763-0b5gwr",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The Solution"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-isurf-canvas-hero": {
      "id": "b-isurf-canvas-hero",
      "type": "canvas",
      "props": {
        "src": "./assets/canvases/interaction-surfaces.canvas.json",
        "title": "One state, two readers",
        "view": "one-state-two-readers"
      },
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpg8ecz-2-cir0id": {
      "id": "pm-mrpg8ecz-2-cir0id",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Every document is a "
        },
        {
          "insert": "doc.json",
          "attributes": {
            "code": true
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": " bundle: an id-keyed tree of blocks — the "
        },
        {
          "insert": "data model",
          "attributes": {
            "reference": {
              "kind": "doc",
              "path": "10-system-design/30-data-model"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": " — serialized to "
        },
        {
          "insert": "serialization",
          "attributes": {
            "reference": {
              "kind": "doc",
              "path": "10-system-design/30-data-model/40-serialization"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": ". "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpg8ecz-3-t6poph": {
      "id": "pm-mrpg8ecz-3-t6poph",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "No reader consumes this form directly"
        },
        {
          "insert": ".",
          "attributes": {
            "bold": true
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": " "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrpg8ecz-4-cdiuzv": {
      "id": "pm-mrpg8ecz-4-cdiuzv",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "It is built for precision, not reading: stable ids make every block addressable, canonical bytes make every change diffable and testable, and the whole tree is validated on every write."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-is2-surfaces-h-2": {
      "id": "b-is2-surfaces-h-2",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The Surfaces"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
